      <title id="aRJQhA">
         <ph id="DAQpwW" props="autonumber">215.371-6</ph> Solicitation provision.</title>
      <conbody id="G8ccHr">
         <p id="1VL3lq">Use the provision at 
               <xref base="i1381391" href="252.215-7007.dita#DFARS_252.215-7007" id="ikPQNY" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">252.215-7007</xref>
            , Notice of Intent to Resolicit, in competitive solicitations, including solicitations using FAR part 12 procedures for the acquisition of commercial items, that will be solicited for fewer than 30 days, unless an exception at 
               <xref base="i1378099" href="215.371-4.dita#DFARS_215.371-4" id="NxlkP7" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">215.371-4</xref>
             applies or the requirement is waived in accordance with 
               <xref base="i1378104" href="215.371-5.dita#DFARS_215.371-5" id="OvcqZI" outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly">215.371-5</xref>
            .</p>
